description:
Supplementary materials for the article "Mycobacterium avium subsp. paratuberculosis (MAP) shedding and seropositivity in youngstock in MAP-infected dairy herds in Alberta, Canada"&nbsp; 
 Supplementary materials include:&nbsp; 
 Supplementary Table 1. Test positive youngstock (&lt;12mo) for MAP using fecal qPCR and serum ELISA across four sampling times in eight dairy herds.&nbsp; 
 Supplementary Figure 1. Proportion of youngstock (&lt;12mo) that were first-time serum ELISA-positive by age.&nbsp; 
 Supplementary Figure 2. Proportion of youngstock (&lt;12mo) that were first-time fecal qPCR-positive by age. 
 &nbsp;

